  "texts": [
    "The DIFMAP pipelines presented in this paper have been updated compared to those used in previous EHT imaging analyses (M 87 * 2017 IV; Sgr A * 2017 III).",
    "We performed a backward compatibility test for these pipelines on the 2017 M 87 * data (April 11, low-band).",
    "We found that the resulting images agree with those presented in M 87 * 2017 IV.",
    "We present the fiducial images of the M 87 * data and the synthetic data in Appendix I.",
    "The Event Horizon Telescope Collaboration: A&A, 681, A79 (2024)"
